          "reviewBody": "Recently I attended my child's Kid fit Day at Raghav Global School. And it was a superb experience. Everything was very well organized by the teachers and the staff. There was no chaos and I and my husband were truly delighted to see our son performing so well. My son studies in Prep Aster and his teacher Ms. Pallavi was encouraging not only him but all the children with so much zeal and love. The Yoga was wonderfully executed by the children. Really want to thank all the teachers for putting so much effort and labor into our kids. It really showed up.",
          "publisher": {
